  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para>
<list>
<item>Determine the direction in which a current-carrying wire experiences a force in an external magnetic field</item>
<item>Calculate the force on a current-carrying wire in an external magnetic field</item>
</list></md:abstract>
  <md:language>en</md:language>
